name: DraftKings
0:
”Alexa, ask DraftKings about Antonio Brown”
”How many points does Drew Brees have?”
”How many DraftKings fantasy points did the Houston Texans have last week?”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: draftkings
des: The DraftKings-Alexa skill allows users to ask Alexa for the most recent fantasy score for a given NFL player. Find out the latest fantasy point totals for any active NFL player by simply opening the DraftKings skill!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
